column1: one^verb^To cause to become one; to gather into a single whole; to unite.^^01
two^noun^The digit/figure 2.^The number 2202 contains three twos.^01
four^noun^The digit or figure 4; an occurrence thereof.^ ^01
five^noun^The digit/figure 5.^He wrote a five followed by four zeroes.^01
seven^noun^The digit/figure 7 or an occurrence thereof.^He wrote three sevens on the paper.^01
ten^noun^A set or group with ten elements.^We divided the chocolates into tens to hand out to Hallowe'en visitors.^01
